text.section:
Within thirty (30) days of the selection of an underwriter or a bond counsel pursuant to this section, the executive director, or his designee, shall appear before the Capital Projects and Bond Oversight Committee to report on the emergency selection. The report shall include:
The materials referred to in subsection 3(a) of this section;
His own description of the bona fide emergency;
The procedure used for selecting the underwriter or bond counsel;
The nature of the services that the underwriter or bond counsel will provide;
The length of time for which the firm will provide these services; and
The costs connected with employing the underwriter or bond counsel.
